            "title": "盤中速報 - 直覺(INTU-US)大跌5%，報343.59美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>直覺(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTU-US</a>)截至台北時間10日23:40股價下跌18.1美元，報343.59美元，跌幅5%，成交量2,792,422（股），盤中最高價360.40美元、最低價343.53美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.35%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.42%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.41%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>直覺(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTU-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-14.39%</li> <li>近 1 月：-23.64%</li> <li>近 3 月：-44.09%</li> <li>近 6 月：-43.92%</li> <li>今年以來：-45.4%</li></ul></section></main>",
